 career. I gained the necessary knowledge, experience and most importantly confidence to return to science and become competitive on an even scale. My Fellowship Advisor pr</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">ovided support throughout my Fellowship. I could focus on retraining and updating my skills in a manner that suited my family. Pfizer had a high quality on-site nursery, which was very important. I had the opportunity to work flexibly (50% hours) while I s</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">tarted to re-establish my scientific credentials.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal"> </span></h1><h1 style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:24pt 0pt 0pt 43.2pt; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">I feel the Daphne Jackson Fellowship has been critical in helping me revive my scientific career. ‘ Dr Judit Mulnar, DJT Fellow sponsored by Pfizer.</span></h1><h1 style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:24pt 0pt 0pt 21.6pt; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.6pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">29</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">‘I recently secured a permanent position, full-time, as</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal"> a senior scientist. Without this fellowship I would not have had the relevant experience or confidence to apply for such a role and I am very grateful for the support of the Trust, my sponsor, supervisor and colleagues. I’m looking forward to the challeng</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">es ahead and feel thoroughly ‘returned’ to a career in science.’ Dr Jackie Ferguson, DJT Fellow sponsored by BBSRC.</span></h1><h1 style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:24pt 0pt 0pt 21.6pt; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.6pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">30</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">‘Going back to work in research part-time has provided me with a new perspective. It has brought sanity back to me as I have a more balanced</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal"> life with personal aspirations added to those that I have for my family members.’ Dr Reyna Al-Ashaab, DJT Fellow sponsored by NERC.</span></h1><h1 style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:24pt 0pt 0pt 21.6pt; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.6pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">31</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">‘I am overjoyed to be back in the lab and am enjoying the new rhythm of life which allows me to be just as much a scientist</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal"> as a mother. I had almost forgotten the excitement of research: new measurements, new data, and discoveries waiting to be unfolded’ Dr Margaret O’Hara, DJT Fellow sponsored by EPSRC.</span></h1><h1 style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:24pt 0pt 0pt 21.6pt; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.6pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">32</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">‘This fellowship has been a major turning point in my career and persona</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">l life’ Dr Malarvizhi Ramesh-Jeyashankar, DJT Fellow sponsored by the BBSRC.</span></h1><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">September 2013</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>